                  Lemma 



\forall n\in\Z_+,\left|\left\{\left\lfloor\frac{n}{1}\right\rfloor,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{2}\right\rfloor,\dots,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{n}\right\rfloor\right\}\right|\in\mathcal{O}(\sqrt n)



                  Proof 



\begin{align}
\left|\left\{\left\lfloor\frac{n}{1}\right\rfloor,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{2}\right\rfloor,\dots,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{n}\right\rfloor\right\}\right|&amp;\le\left|\left\{\left\lfloor\frac{n}{d}\right\rfloor:d\in\{1,2,\dots,\lfloor\sqrt n\rfloor\}\right\}\right|+\left|\left\{\left\lfloor\frac{n}{1}\right\rfloor,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{2}\right\rfloor,\dots,\left\lfloor\frac{n}{n}\right\rfloor\right\}\cap\{1,2,\dots,\lfloor\sqrt n\rfloor\}\right|\\
